## 4. File & Folder Organization (MANDATORY)

### Folder strategy: **By Feature**, not by type

Each feature owns:

* its screens
* its components
* its hooks
* its logic

### Example structure

```
src/
 ├── app/
 │   ├── navigation/
 │   └── App.tsx
 ├── features/
 │   ├── invitation/
 │   │   ├── screens/
 │   │   │   ├── InvitationViewScreen.tsx
 │   │   │   └── RsvpSubmitScreen.tsx
 │   │   ├── components/
 │   │   │   ├── RsvpForm.tsx
 │   │   │   └── GuestCountPicker.tsx
 │   │   ├── hooks/
 │   │   │   └── useRsvp.ts
 │   │   ├── api/
 │   │   │   └── invitationQueries.ts
 │   │   └── types.ts
 │   └── auth/
 │       ├── screens/
 │       └── hooks/
 ├── shared/
 │   ├── components/
 │   ├── hooks/
 │   ├── utils/
 │   └── theme/
 └── types/
```

### Rules

* Screens **must not** import from other feature folders
* Shared components go in `/shared`
* No circular dependencies
* No deep relative imports (`../../../`)

